name: IteratorUtils_matchesAllTest
description: Unit tests for the IteratorUtils.matchesAll method.

test_cases.name: testMatchesAll_AllElementsMatch
test_cases.description: Tests that IteratorUtils.matchesAll returns true when all elements in the iterator match the predicate.

test_cases.name: testMatchesAll_NotAllElementsMatch
test_cases.description: Tests that IteratorUtils.matchesAll returns false when not all elements in the iterator match the predicate.

test_cases.name: testMatchesAll_NullIterator
test_cases.description: Tests that IteratorUtils.matchesAll returns true when the iterator is null.

test_cases.name: testMatchesAll_NullPredicate
test_cases.description: Tests that IteratorUtils.matchesAll throws a NullPointerException when the predicate is null.
